{"tid":930162,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE「撒嬌三行詩」徹底擊潰李光洙！　娜璉放大絕：幫我呼呼～","createTime":"2018-12-06T06:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T10:08:55.000Z","uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fe48468c2b5e41a9f8b5a272424569b008cc2d02","tid":930162,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:08:25.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE再度出演《Running Man》，之前出演時，TWICE的撒嬌魅力讓主持群及觀眾無法抵擋，這次出演娜璉應劉在錫要求上演一段「宋智孝三行詩」，3句話徹底擊潰李光洙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3743/d3743283.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3743%2Fd3743283.jpg&h=4fb1cb2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼娜璉撒嬌，擊潰李光洙。（圖／翻攝自愛奇藝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3743/d3743282.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3743%2Fd3743282.jpg&h=831bcbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n娜璉的「宋智孝三行詩」，「宋」開頭用小朋友發音不準確的撒嬌方式造句：「手幾頭（手指頭）好痛。」一開頭就無預警用娃娃音撒嬌瞬間讓人手指捲曲，李光洙腿軟：「我還沒準備好啊！」輪到「智」，她向李光洙招招手說：「現在光洙哥你過來！」李光洙帶著滿臉笑意走近。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3743/d3743284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3743%2Fd3743284.jpg&h=4574c235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼娜璉撒嬌，擊潰李光洙。（圖／翻攝自愛奇藝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3743/d3743285.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3743%2Fd3743285.jpg&h=89dec2ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第三個字「孝」娜璉直接放大絕：「幫我呼呼（狀聲詞與孝韓文雷同）。」陷入撒嬌魅力中的李光洙防線瞬間被擊潰，「容陷愛（容易陷入愛情）」人設上身，抓著她的手猛吹氣，結果引來劉在錫、池錫辰等人一陣暴打。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g186WiW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg186WiW.jpg&h=4050342f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzE2uDX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzE2uDX.jpg&h=26a92c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望娜璉隻手乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc184cfd2990e53faacc1c47b1cc865389bf3596","tid":930162,"uid":46435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"咕咕嘎嘎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6d8680cc0186fd7dc702edf764b61ae3dc027b","tid":930162,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"李光洙真係好似坤狗係女都㗳糖"},{"pid":"3deeeebe495bacf6b72e807e873a1c04f50b896e","tid":930162,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca9d11a6309a1cbf53f117d16cfb8a3ebd67ca6","tid":930162,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:48:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">😍</span>"},{"pid":"ce8393d7bc0746e50f9dd1b7c68856fb45ffa023","tid":930162,"uid":190328,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7f6d8680cc0186fd7dc702edf764b61ae3dc027b","tid":930162,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"李光洙真係好似坤狗係女都㗳糖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"扮下野姐，條女咁樣衰點會有feel啊"},{"pid":"201519cb6fcb3812a88c8392e325b1228a9c5ed9","tid":930162,"uid":66549,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"ce8393d7bc0746e50f9dd1b7c68856fb45ffa023","tid":930162,"uid":190328,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7f6d8680cc0186fd7dc702edf764b61ae3dc027b","tid":930162,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"李光洙真係好似坤狗係女都㗳糖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"扮下野姐，條女咁樣衰點會有feel啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T10:01:26.000Z","msg":"睇綜藝咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e16f0a3f5fc8